              Founded in 2015, Life School is a non-profit organization directly under UNESCO Vietnam. The Life School was established for the purpose of offering services to people in five main areas: 
1. Self Discovery, Self Awareness in relationship with real life;
2. Developing personal potential in a spirit of service to the community;
3. Improving quality of relationships and healing emotions;
4. Whole person Healthy Living – physical, vital, emotional, mental and spiritual; 
5. Social responsibility & Values based Leadership.
